{"id":"bera","term":"Bera","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Gift, or son of evil, king of Sodom at the time of the invasion of the four kings under Chedorlaomer (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 14:2\">Gen. 14:2</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 14:8\">8</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 14:17\">17</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 14:21\">21</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 14:2","Genesis 14:8","Genesis 14:17","Genesis 14:21"]}